/**********************************************************************************
@file freertos_cpp_wrappers_config.hpp.in
@author Andrey V. Shchekin <aschokin@gmail.com>
@brief CMake-generated configuration header for FreeRTOS C++ Wrappers
@version 3.1.0
@date 2026-04-21

This file is processed by CMake's configure_file() command.
All @VARIABLE@ placeholders are substituted with values from
the CMake cache. When this header is not generated (e.g.,
header-only usage without CMake), sensible defaults are
provided via preprocessor fallbacks.
**********************************************************************************/

